American Fltrona Corp said its boardauthorized the repurchase of up to 100,000 shares of company'sstock for use in the its employee benefit plans and for othergeneral corporate purposes.    The company had 3,690,000 shares outstanding as ofSeptember 30.    American also said it declared a regular quarterly dividendof 19 cts a share payable November 25 to shareholders of recordNovember 10. Reuter&#3;